the length of cell dm.
</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/171389/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" targetBox="[393,1219,615,1361]" targetPageId="3">
<paragraph blockId="3.[264,1322,1387,1480]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
