</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[884,966,1388,1411]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
1, phallus with hypandrium, ventral view; 2, phallus lateral view; 3, subepandrial sclerite and surstylus (ventral, left); 4, ejaculatory apodeme; 5, epandrium lateral view showing anal projection (ap); 6, head dorsal view; 7, wing.
